Package Library

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Book
    The Book class is where four variables of a book is stored for being used in the Library.
    Date
    The Date class is used to hold a date with the variables: year, month, and day.
    Kiosk
    The Kiosk class is used for processing commands from the console.
    Library
    The Library class creates a library object used for storing books.
    Month
    The Month class is used to consolidate the constant month variables used by the Date class.
    RunProject1
    Driver class for library, initiates the Kiosk class.
